Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.48,0:01:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（藤隆在大学过夜）\N（桃矢打工2天不在小樱户外旅游）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.33,0:01:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一个人看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心被人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.74,0:01:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃很多…\N很多小樱帮我准备好的零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.85,0:02:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天吃冰淇淋真是过瘾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱现在大概正在\N这种雪白的雪地里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的滑着雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.97,0:02:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第64话 小樱与大风雪的滑雪课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了喔\N下一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你滑得真好，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是终于不会跌倒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你才是真的很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只溜冰溜得好\N滑雪也滑得这么棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我母亲从小就教我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这是你头一次学滑雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师才教你一个钟头而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是艾瑞尔吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔你好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的夸奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是什么都会耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪也好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才厉害，进步得好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到滑雪啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是用木屐滑雪的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木屐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用木屐要怎么滑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋齿的部份会阻碍，不能滑耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N以前的木屐没有鞋齿的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对，柊泽同学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.95,0:04:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，而且前后大约各有1公尺长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前还有滑雪用的木屐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说平常也是穿那种的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不下雪时也穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以据说走路非常辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想走快，必须要有秘诀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.94,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天时还有\N看谁穿那种木屐走得快的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天当然是在雪上举行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木屐滑雪运动大会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连柊泽同学都跟他一起在瞎掰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下真不知道该不该阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们两个还真有默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更厉害的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.45,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果直冲过去，他会撞到树的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柊泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.69,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在只是经验不够而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以做得更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是滑雪，其他的也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上次也是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱到了下午好像就很会滑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.12,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子你也是学了一天\N就滑得很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是山崎教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道吗？说到滑雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N自由时间还让你帮我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会，因为我喜欢做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没帮利佳的忙，这样好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说她一个人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到雪山的夜晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要说鬼故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又特地去找来了\N跟这里有关的鬼故事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找是找了，可是找不到好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.91,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，有没有人知道\N关于滑雪场的鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到滑雪场…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要听瞎掰\N我们要听鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柊泽同学，你知不知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英国应该有很多灵异小说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就说一个关于雪山的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.02,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冬天的雪山\N刚才还很晴朗的天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说有时候会突然乌云密布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，从山上刮起冷风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始下起雪\N而雪越下越大时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说会出现雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.18,0:09:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说雪女会造成雪崩\N将碰到的人全部冻死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个情节跟日本的很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，因为这是日本的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是外国的故事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们难得来到了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得说个\N跟这里符合的故事比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.84,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不过\N那不是这个滑雪场的故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是在这一带流传的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天要早起，该去睡觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶，已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，柊泽同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.73,0:10:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后再说鬼故事给我们听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能见到她就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定她非常的漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被冰冻起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个故事不怎么可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，已经够可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.06,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，原来你很怕听鬼故事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你早点说就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是奈绪子好像很爱听鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有什么害怕的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才想问你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.25,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，今天谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.69,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很害怕\N所以你才提议大家去睡觉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.63,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每次总是对我说\N“我并不是…”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实不是那样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么会那么想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你人很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去外面看一下好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冰喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N你好像也做过一个熊宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送人了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.34,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望雪兔哥会愿意收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被他所拥有的\N月亮的力量所吸引而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.89,0:14:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我喜欢的是别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真正喜欢的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像问了不该问的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.10,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的，我们进屋里去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你进步很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个，李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.86,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，李也滑得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是自由时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在中午之前，你们自己滑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本跟李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.98,0:15:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们去滑难一点的中难度路线\N应该也没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过别太逞强喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.72,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，怎么样？\N要上去看看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.73,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李同学也真的很了不起\N才学一天就滑得那么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.67,0:16:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼的运动神经真的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.28,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才会跌倒\N跟运动神经似乎没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，要休息一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想再滑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我想去滑滑看\N中难度路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，你要不要一起去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在下面等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我特地带摄影机来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要制作一卷\N“小樱飞舞在银白山中”的专辑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你一起滑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪好像越下越大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还很晴朗的天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说有时候会突然乌云密布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，从山上刮起冷风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.32,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始下起雪\N而雪越下越大时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说会出现雪女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像要刮大风雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视线不良很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.05,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就坐缆车直接下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快，快进去休息木屋\N快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个情景跟柊泽同学\N昨天说的故事好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱跟柊泽同学呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像没来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个都还在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在里面，而且上了锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还很晴朗的天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然乌云密布，开始下起雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而雪越下越大时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.29,0:19:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想说这种天气\N好像雪女会出现的天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N我没想到你会那么害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道我就不说那种故事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我自己太胆小\N是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雪崩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快点逃走才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面的建筑物会被埋在雪里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得想想办法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾瑞尔在我旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用睡牌让他睡着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我背不动艾瑞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.66,0:20:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他睡着了\N说不定会被风雪吹走而受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.33,0:20:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果离开他，他一定会担心我\N而跑来找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好用那张牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下，艾瑞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛创造的库洛牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃旧有姿态\N重新转生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以新主人，小樱之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“时”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在时间停止的这段期间内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得快想办法阻止雪崩才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“火”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.00,0:22:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道小樱他们要不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.41,0:22:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，老师去找他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在这里等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.35,0:22:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.59,0:22:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柊泽同学也跟她在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.56,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.36,0:22:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎有点累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扶她回房间休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.67,0:22:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.14,0:23:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.08,0:23:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是让你难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.65,0:23:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是短时间内这也是不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.30,0:24:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次哥哥的学校要举行校庆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.24,0:24:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年他们好像要拍电影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.90,0:24:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到那部电影也要找我演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.34,0:24:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥好像也会参加演出\N我一定要加油才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.91,0:24:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使\N“小樱、雪兔与消失的力量”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.62,0:24:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起\N解除封印！
